{
  "stem": "964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So these people, they didn't take to the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I knew that he, for sure, he's alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I met my brother in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when he came to the States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, when he came to the States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no opportunity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no money to go to-- to Israel to see him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so when he came to the States, I sent him out papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, on this-- [INAUDIBLE] a relative, was easier for him to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was already established, so he came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's how I met my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If the war would have lasted another six months, I wouldn't have been here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was impossible, because they-- they became so efficient in-- in the extermination, catching Jews, that you couldn't get.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If anybody remained alive, he would have remain a Pole or anything else with intermarriages or something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And second, I would like to give a message that, if ever happened a Holocaust in the United States, people should arm themself and-- and fight to the last.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because if-- it was the case in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't the partisans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the partisans, if the Germans knew that these people have arms, they were very careful.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't go like to a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Poland, the Poles drag old Jews, old women, they drag them out from-- from under the ground, so to speak, in order to give them to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they got a price for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if now, anything should happen, any Jew, if he does not arm himself, is-- is lost.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think this should be the-- the lesson.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
